Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.58,0:00:02.34,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.26,Transcription,,0,0,0,,This is a demo of a new tool called WhisperSub.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.64,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Using this tool, you can extract audio from MKV files
Dialogue: 2,0:00:09.64,0:00:13.06,Transcription,,0,0,0,,automatically, perform transcription,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:13.06,0:00:16.34,Transcription,,0,0,0,,and merge subtitles.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:17.26,0:00:19.42,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, it supports multiple languages
Dialogue: 2,0:00:19.42,0:00:21.62,Transcription,,0,0,0,,and can automatically convert to romanized
Dialogue: 2,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.96,Transcription,,0,0,0,,text, making it very convenient.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:24.70,0:00:26.60,Transcription,,0,0,0,,It can also process noisy audio
Dialogue: 2,0:00:26.60,0:00:29.34,Transcription,,0,0,0,,as it includes voice separation functionality.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.49,0:00:31.06,Transcription,,0,0,0,,Please give it a try.